This is a web-based course which is designed for students who want to better understand and use tenses in  English grammar. Each tense group is followed by a number of exercises which help students to better use theory in practice.Objectives/eesmärkid:  The aim of the course is to help learners understand the tense system of English grammar either in the active voice. After each tense group the learner  has to complete a number of practical tasks in order to better learn the material.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  Upon the completion of the course the student: 1) understands the system of grammar tenses in English;  2) can recognize different tense forms, is able to form different tense forms and use them in proper context.
